{"type": "article", "id": 30552, "title": "姜汁啤酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-03T23:04:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160803231800OKAqhLW1fBR5b0py.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>菲律宾的精酿姜汁啤酒品牌 FICO 委托 <a href=\"http://www.designbyshao.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shao</a> 工作室设计了一组非常清新的包装。Shao 的设计师们采用了透明的瓶身，让人们可以清楚地看到啤酒的颜色，并通过简洁的白底黑字标签强调这一自产品牌所特有的“有机感”。为了区别四种不同的风味，融合了原材料颜色的圆圈代替了字母 O 出现在标签上，是一个非常有心的小细节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234531Of1yDAiThjM2B7JP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234530LpT1r6YSGuz0Kq4m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234531OnaRI24TD6fQruWg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234531HT2GsU453waRWytL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}